{"tid":2081101,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"老母買咗個麒麟果返嚟","createTime":"2020-06-27T03:05:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-27T10:59:10.000Z","uid":322046,"like":8,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"1961fc7fe61541933937be15ac27c010786b2b1f","tid":2081101,"uid":322046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T03:05:39.000Z","msg":"前晚端午節老母叫咗一班親戚返嚟打牌<br />\n食完飯老母就去咗切生果 <br />\n切咗譚仔咁大個碗嘅火龍果拎出嚟之後佢就去咗廁所唔知搞乜<br />\n然後啲親戚個個都唔食生果咁吉咗一兩舊就繼續去打牌<br />\n咁我一路打機又口痕咁咪一路打一路食<br />\n食下食下都食咗一大半<br />\n呢個時候老母終於喺廁所出嚟<br />\n<br />\n我：咦啲火龍果甜過平時嗰啲咁多嘅<br />\n<br />\n老母：係咩，等我試下先，真係好甜喎<br />\n<br />\n我：喺邊買㗎，下次可以再買喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n老母：樓下嗰間咋嘛，佢話呢隻甜啲㗎，不過黃色嘅，果然冇呃我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我聽到已經嚇到面都青埋，望一望個碗得返三份一咁多嘅麒麟果<br />\n<br />\n我：黃色咪即係麒麟果囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n老母：唔係嚟㗎，佢話呢隻叫唔知咩果，死喇唔記得名添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後，我尋日屙撚到今朝屙到屎忽都損埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb250e584ae036de33266f60529582fb169cfd41","tid":2081101,"uid":177089,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T03:12:10.000Z","msg":"7/10 故事內容生動 惟描述較平舖直敘 宜使用更多修辭手法"},{"pid":"fc0a2afba27a5a5cb42d52e07b7029320eac4069","tid":2081101,"uid":322046,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"bb250e584ae036de33266f60529582fb169cfd41","tid":2081101,"uid":177089,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T03:12:10.000Z","msg":"7/10 故事內容生動 惟描述較平舖直敘 宜使用更多修辭手法"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T03:13:10.000Z","msg":"屙到屎眼都就爛俾多幾分同情分啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bfef27ffda4a7c8f0857645da771b6fc5c6ee5f","tid":2081101,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fc0a2afba27a5a5cb42d52e07b7029320eac4069","tid":2081101,"uid":322046,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"bb250e584ae036de33266f60529582fb169cfd41","tid":2081101,"uid":177089,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T03:12:10.000Z","msg":"7/10 故事內容生動 惟描述較平舖直敘 宜使用更多修辭手法"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T03:13:10.000Z","msg":"屙到屎眼都就爛俾多幾分同情分啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T03:15:13.000Z","msg":"已經俾咗語癌同情分"},{"pid":"ae0cf3494118c61634edefd97fb4dfc079133634","tid":2081101,"uid":13049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T04:26:26.000Z","msg":"我老母都試過買麒麟果當咗火龍果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食完先知係麒麟果<br />\n第二日屙到七彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9500cb54b6837280533afc75544864da6118ab72","tid":2081101,"uid":115579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T04:29:16.000Z","msg":"點解上一代咁鐘意食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />??"},{"pid":"6b65aa3cfc3c921cfc8f4c0f764471f38cc66787","tid":2081101,"uid":322046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9500cb54b6837280533afc75544864da6118ab72","tid":2081101,"uid":115579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T04:29:16.000Z","msg":"點解上一代咁鐘意食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />??"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T04:31:38.000Z","msg":"我呀公話通便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但我覺得好似食瀉藥咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"478cf93801fb0683c2c1bc051a3f5fa33c1a2b11","tid":2081101,"uid":1928,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T04:33:42.000Z